title: The New Yorker magazine - September 16 (pdf, printable)
description:
The New Yorker magazine - September 16th, 2013

90 Pages | PDF | English | 46.4 MB 


The New Yorker offers a signature mix of reporting and commentary on politics, international affairs, and the arts, along with fiction, poetry, humor, and cartoons.

This pdf is full-page full-content scan (as opposed to my "compressed" torrents where speed is priority, thus full-page advertisements and the town-specific "Goings On About Town" sections are left out, but still, their quality is not compromised.)
